<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٦٩٤ -<span class="c5"> حدَّثنا أَبُو مَعْمَرٍ:</span> حدَّثنا عَبْدُ الْوَارِثِ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>حدَّثنا أَيُّوبُ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ عِكْرِمَةَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ قَالَ:</span> احْتَجَمَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> وَهوَ صَائِمٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>